  body
    header
      a(href="#details") Our Wedding
      a(href="#story") Our Story
      a(href="#india") Experience India
      a(href="#clothing") What to Wear

    .section#intro
      p.date October 25-27th, 2018 | Hyderabad, India
      h1
        | Ashna &amp; Brett
      a#primary-rsvp(href="#") RSVP

    .section.details
      a.section-anchor#details
      .day#day1
        img.icon(src="/images/falaknuma.jpg")
        h2 Pellikoduka
        p.date Thursday, October 25th
        p.description This traditional ceremony is intended to prepare the bride and groom for their wedding, and is open to all guests
        p.location Falaknuma Palace
      .day#day2
        img.icon(src="/images/hyderabad.jpg")
        h2 Sangeeth
        p.date Friday, October 26th
        p.description The Sangeeth takes place the eve before the wedding day and is a night filled with music, laughter, dance, and food
        p.location Another location here
      .day#day3
        img.icon(src="/images/ceremony.jpeg")
        h2 Pelli
        p.date Saturday, October 27th
        p.description The official wedding ceremony, with an intimate dinner reception afterwards to celebrate the couple
        p.location Falaknuma Palace
        
    .section.story
      a.section-anchor#story
      h2.section-title Our Story
      ul#timeline
        li.left
          img(src="/images/brett.jpeg")
          p
            span.year 1996
            br
            | About 27 years ago, Brett was born in Los Gatos, California
          .dot
        li.right
          img(src="/images/hyderabad.jpg")
          p 
            span.year 2008
            br
            | Brett went to college to become an enginerd and Ashna went off to a one of those artsy-fartsy schools
          .dot
        li.left
          img(src="/images/brett.jpeg")
          p 
            span.year 2012
            br
            | Brett graduated from MIT and moved to SF to do start-uppy things
          .dot
        li.right
          img(src="/images/toast.jpeg")
          p 
            span.year 2012
            br
            | Ashna graduated from Yale and moved to NYC to do business-y things
          .dot
        li.left
          img(src="/images/ceremony.jpeg")
          p In May 2017, they went to Japan and brett proposed
          .dot
        li.right
          img(src="/images/ceremony.jpeg")
          p In August 2017, they went to see the eclipse in Portland and have an engagement ceremony
          .dot
        li.spacer
      #timeline-centerpiece
        img(src="/images/ashnaandbrett.jpeg")
        p And now, they're getting married! It's super exciting!
      
